thread.title: Rand Paul to hold rally in Denver before GOP debate
thread.title_full: Rand Paul to hold rally in Denver before GOP debate - The Denver Post

author: The Associated Press
title: Rand Paul to hold rally in Denver before GOP debate
text:
DENVER (AP) â€” Sen. Rand Paul will campaign in Denver in advance of the Republican presidential debate in Boulder.
Paul will hold a rally at the University of Colorado's Denver campus on Tuesday at 4 p.m. The debate is Wednesday night at CU's campus in Boulder.
Paul is one of 10 candidates who will share the stage for the primetime debate sponsored by CNBC.
